data.description: Don't miss out on this 3BR, 2BA Brick Ranch in Kennedy Twp. Montour School District. This Home offers many updates including the Kitchen/newer appliances, roof, AC unit & Washer. The main floor has a cozy LR with Fireplace, Kitchen that opens into the DR. Lots of  natural light throughout. The lower level has a finished Basement with a full Bath that has the potential to be a 4th BR or Family Room.  The Laundry Room leads out to a large Backyard surrounded by lots of trees and wildlife. At the end of the yard is a private fire pit, great for fall nights. There are two Fruit trees - Peach & Pear on the property. The two car Tandem Garage is a plus with plenty of storage or room for a workshop.
